  "ai_usage": "Use for skincare, wellness, tea, eco, and sustainable brands. The calm comes from earthy tones, organic blob shapes (asymmetric border-radius), and a serif/sans pairing with airy spacing. Recolor via --leaf/--clay/--cream. Drop product/botanical photos into the blob frames. Reduced-motion safe.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/organic-wellness.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Organic / Nature — Wellness Brand</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"organic-wellness\",\n  \"title\": \"Organic / Nature — Wellness Brand\",\n  \"summary\": \"A calm botanical skincare/wellness page: earthy palette, organic blob frames, soft serif headings, and an ingredient-led layout.\",\n  \"description\": \"Organic, nature-led design pairs earthy tones with soft organic shapes and botanical calm — perfect for skincare, wellness, and sustainable brands. This page uses leaf-green and clay tones, asymmetric blob-masked imagery, a soft serif/sans pairing, an ingredients grid, and a gentle ritual section.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"ecommerce\", \"brand\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"organic\", \"nature\", \"wellness\", \"skincare\", \"earthy\", \"botanical\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"beginner\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers (CSS border-radius blobs).\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"Organic shapes via border-radius; a slow blob morph; gradient placeholders for product. No images or libraries.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Warm earthy contrast preserved; focus-visible; blob morph stops under reduced-motion.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"--leaf / --clay / --cream\", \"description\": \"Earthy palette\", \"default\": \"green / terracotta / cream\" },\n    { \"name\": \"blob radius\", \"description\": \"Asymmetric border-radius\", \"default\": \"organic\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Cooler sage palette\", \"Real botanical photography in the blobs\", \"Add a product carousel\"],\n  \"related\": [\"blob-morph\", \"soft-serif\", \"reveal-on-scroll\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for skincare, wellness, tea, eco, and sustainable brands. The calm comes from earthy tones, organic blob shapes (asymmetric border-radius), and a serif/sans pairing with airy spacing. Recolor via --leaf/--clay/--cream. Drop product/botanical photos into the blob frames. Reduced-motion safe.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--cream:#f3efe4;--cream2:#e9e3d2;--ink:#2c3a2e;--muted:#6f7a68;--leaf:#5b7b52;--leaf2:#789a63;--clay:#c08457;\n    --serif:\"Fraunces\",\"Georgia\",serif;--sans:\"Inter\",system-ui,sans-serif;--blob:62% 38% 55% 45%/55% 48% 52% 45%;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}\n  body{margin:0;background:var(--cream);color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--sans);line-height:1.7}\n  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n  .wrap{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem}\n  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:80px}\n  .brand{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em}\n  .links{display:flex;gap:1.5rem;align-items:center;color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem}.links a:hover{color:var(--ink)}\n  .btn{display:inline-block;background:var(--leaf);color:var(--cream);border:none;border-radius:999px;padding:.7rem 1.5rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:background .25s,transform .15s}\n  .btn:hover{background:var(--leaf2);transform:translateY(-2px)}\n  .btn.ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--ink);border:1.5px solid var(--leaf)}\n  .btn:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--clay);outline-offset:3px}\n  .hero{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center;padding:3rem 0 5rem}\n  .ey{color:var(--clay);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.76rem}\n  h1{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:500;font-size:clamp(2.6rem,6vw,4.6rem);line-height:1.04;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:1rem 0 .8rem}\n  h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--leaf)}\n  .hero p{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.15rem;max-width:40ch;margin:0 0 1.8rem}\n  .ctas{display:flex;gap:.8rem;flex-wrap:wrap}\n  .blobimg{aspect-ratio:1;border-radius:var(--blob);background:linear-gradient(150deg,var(--leaf2),var(--clay));animation:morph 14s ease-in-out infinite;box-shadow:0 30px 60px rgba(91,123,82,.25)}\n  @keyframes morph{50%{border-radius:42% 58% 45% 55%/52% 42% 58% 48%}}\n  section{padding:5rem 0}\n  h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:500;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);text-align:center;margin:0 0 .5rem}\n  .lead{color:var(--muted);text-align:center;max-width:48ch;margin:0 auto 2.6rem}\n  .ings{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.6rem}\n  .ing{background:var(--cream2);border-radius:24px;padding:2rem 1.5rem;text-align:center}\n  .ing .leaf{width:64px;height:64px;margin:0 auto 1rem;border-radius:50% 50% 50% 6px;transform:rotate(45deg);background:linear-gradient(145deg,var(--leaf2),var(--leaf))}\n  .ing h3{font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:500;margin:0 0 .3rem;font-size:1.25rem}.ing p{color:var(--muted);margin:0;font-size:.95rem}\n  .ritual{background:var(--leaf);color:var(--cream);border-radius:36px;padding:3.5rem 2rem}\n  .ritual h2{color:var(--cream)}.ritual .steps{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2rem}\n  .ritual .step{text-align:center}.ritual .step .n{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:2.4rem;opacity:.6}.ritual .step p{opacity:.9;margin:.3rem 0 0}\n  .cta{text-align:center}\n  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--cream2);color:var(--muted);text-align:center;padding:2.5rem 0 3rem;font-size:.9rem}\n  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);transition:opacity .8s,transform .8s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1)}.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}\n  @media(max-width:820px){.hero{grid-template-columns:1fr}.ings,.ritual .steps{grid-template-columns:1fr}.links a:not(.btn){display:none}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.blobimg{animation:none}.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <nav>\n      <div class=\"brand\">Verda</div>\n      <div class=\"links\"><a href=\"#\">Shop</a><a href=\"#\">Ingredients</a><a href=\"#\">Ritual</a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Shop now</a></div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n      <div>\n        <p class=\"ey\">Botanical skincare</p>\n        <h1>Skin that <em>remembers</em> the wild.</h1>\n        <p>Cold-pressed botanicals and nothing you can't pronounce. Kind to your skin, kinder to the earth.</p>\n        <div class=\"ctas\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Discover the range</a><a class=\"btn ghost\" href=\"#\">Our story</a></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"blobimg\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Product on botanicals\"></div>\n    </header>\n  </div>\n\n  <section><div class=\"wrap\">\n    <h2 class=\"reveal\">Grown, not formulated</h2>\n    <p class=\"lead reveal\">Every drop begins on a farm, not in a lab. These are the roots of our range.</p>\n    <div class=\"ings\">\n      <div class=\"ing reveal\"><div class=\"leaf\"></div><h3>Sea buckthorn</h3><p>Omega-rich oil that restores and protects the skin barrier.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"ing reveal\"><div class=\"leaf\"></div><h3>Blue tansy</h3><p>Calms redness and quiets stressed, reactive skin.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"ing reveal\"><div class=\"leaf\"></div><h3>Rosehip</h3><p>Brightens and softens fine lines, naturally.</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </div></section>\n\n  <section><div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"ritual reveal\">\n    <h2>The evening ritual</h2>\n    <div class=\"steps\">\n      <div class=\"step\"><div class=\"n\">01</div><p>Cleanse with the oil balm to melt the day away.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"step\"><div class=\"n\">02</div><p>Press in three drops of the restoring serum.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"step\"><div class=\"n\">03</div><p>Seal with the night cream and breathe.</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </div></div></section>\n\n  <section><div class=\"wrap cta reveal\">\n    <h2>Begin your ritual</h2>\n    <p class=\"lead\">Try the full range risk-free for 30 nights. Love it or your money back.</p>\n    <a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Shop the collection 🌿</a>\n  </div></section>\n\n  <footer>© <span id=\"yr\"></span> Verda · Cruelty-free · Carbon-neutral · Refillable</footer>\n  <script>\n    document.getElementById('yr').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();\n    var io=new IntersectionObserver(function(es){es.forEach(function(e){if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('in');io.unobserve(e.target)}})},{threshold:.12});\n    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function(el){io.observe(el)});\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
